msgstr "Scheduler queries each schedule element for upcoming tasks and generates a queue of events that should be executed within a short period of time. After the period has been expired or new schedule event was added/removed, events queue is being automatically refreshed. Thus, scheduler scans schedule element objects and accesses storage only when the queue refresh is required."

